Enum Flag

    public enum Flag
extends java.lang.Enum<Flag>
implements java.util.function.Predicate<org.telegram.telegrambots.api.objects.Update>
    Flags are an conditions that are applied on an Update.

    They can be used on Ability.AbilityBuilder.flag(Flag...) and on the post conditions in Ability.AbilityBuilder.reply(Consumer, Predicate[]).
